PN,30201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775624629
OL,3,CTrump agrees to halt bombing of Iran
OL,4,Cfor two weeks subject to strait
OL,5,Creopening
OL,7,FDonald Trump has agreed to a
OL,8,Fprovisional two-week ceasefire in the
OL,9,FIran war after pulling back at the
OL,10,Flast-minute from his apocalyptic
OL,11,Fwarning that "a whole civilisation
OL,12,Fwill die" unless Tehran met his
OL,13,Fdemands.
OL,15,FLess than two hours before his
OL,16,Fdeadline passed for Iran to agree a
OL,17,Fdeal, the US president said he was
OL,18,Fsuspending his threat to widen the
OL,19,Fmilitary offensive to power plants and
OL,20,Fbridges subject to the reopening of
OL,21,Fthe critical Strait of Hormuz waterway.
OL,26,@sD@NOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
