FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775624629
OL,3,CTrump agrees to halt bombing of Iran
OL,4,Cfor two weeks subject to strait
OL,5,Creopening
OL,7,FHe said Tehran proposed a 10-point
OL,8,Fplan that provided "a workable basis
OL,9,Fon which to negotiate".
OL,11,FThe move followed a request by
OL,12,FPakistan, which has been acting as a
OL,13,Fmediator in the conflict between the
OL,14,Fwarring sides.
OL,16,FThe Iranian regime said it had
OL,17,Faccepted a temporary truce but warned
OL,18,Fthat its "hands remain upon the
OL,19,Ftrigger", while a White House official
OL,20,Fsaid Israel had also accepted the
OL,21,Fterms of the ceasefire agreement.
OL,26,@pD@TOUqD@VO]zD@JOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
