OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775624629
OL,3,CTrump agrees to halt bombing of Iran
OL,4,Cfor two weeks subject to strait
OL,5,Creopening
OL,7,FIsraeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,8,FNetanyahu said Israel backed Mr
OL,9,FTrump's suspension of strikes against
OL,10,FIran, but said any deal does not cover
OL,11,Ffighting against Hezbollah in Lebanon.
OL,13,FPakistan Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif
OL,14,Fsaid he had invited Iranian and US
OL,15,Fofficials to Islamabad for talks on
OL,16,FFriday.
OL,18,FThe US president had given Tehran
OL,19,Funtil 1am on Wednesday UK time to end
OL,20,Fits chokehold on the strait or face
OL,21,Fannihilation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
