FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775624629
OL,3,CTrump agrees to halt bombing of Iran
OL,4,Cfor two weeks subject to strait
OL,5,Creopening
OL,7,FWriting on his Truth Social platform,
OL,8,FMr Trump said: "Based on conversations
OL,9,Fwith Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif and
OL,10,FField Marshal Asim Munir, of Pakistan,
OL,11,Fand wherein they requested that I hold
OL,12,Foff the destructive force being sent
OL,13,Ftonight to Iran, and subject to the
OL,14,FIslamic Republic of Iran agreeing to
OL,15,Fthe COMPLETE, IMMEDIATE, and SAFE
OL,16,FOPENING of the Strait of Hormuz, I
OL,17,Fagree to suspend the bombing and
OL,18,Fattack of Iran for a period of two
OL,19,Fweeks.
OL,26,@pD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
