PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775624629
OL,3,CTrump agrees to halt bombing of Iran
OL,4,Cfor two weeks subject to strait
OL,5,Creopening
OL,7,F"This will be a double sided
OL,8,FCEASEFIRE! The reason for doing so is
OL,9,Fthat we have already met and exceeded
OL,10,Fall Military objectives, and are very
OL,11,Ffar along with a definitive Agreement
OL,12,Fconcerning Longterm PEACE with Iran,
OL,13,Fand PEACE in the Middle East."
OL,15,FHe added: "We received a 10 point
OL,16,Fproposal from Iran, and believe it is
OL,17,Fa workable basis on which to negotiate.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@^O]wD@KOU
