OL,3,CTrump agrees to halt bombing of Iran
OL,4,Cfor two weeks subject to strait
OL,5,Creopening
OL,7,F"Almost all of the various points of
OL,8,Fpast contention have been agreed to
OL,9,Fbetween the United States and Iran,
OL,10,Fbut a two week period will allow the
OL,11,FAgreement to be finalized and
OL,12,Fconsummated.
OL,14,F"On behalf of the United States of
OL,15,FAmerica, as President, and also
OL,16,Frepresenting the Countries of the
OL,17,FMiddle East, it is an Honor to have
OL,18,Fthis Longterm problem close to
OL,19,Fresolution. Thank you for your
OL,20,Fattention to this matter! President
OL,21,FDONALD J. TRUMP"
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU}D@PO]
