OL,4,Cfor two weeks subject to strait
OL,5,Creopening
OL,7,FIran's Supreme National Security
OL,8,FCouncil said it would negotiate with
OL,9,Fthe US in Pakistan's capital,
OL,10,FIslamabad, starting on Friday.
OL,12,FBut while accepting a ceasefire, it
OL,13,Fsaid in a statement: "It is emphasised
OL,14,Fthat this does not signify the
OL,15,Ftermination of the war.
OL,17,F"Our hands remain upon the trigger,
OL,18,Fand should the slightest error be
OL,19,Fcommitted by the enemy, it shall be
OL,20,Fmet with full force."
OL,26,@uD@VOUyD@AOU|D@UO]
