OL,3,CTrump agrees to halt bombing of Iran
OL,4,Cfor two weeks subject to strait
OL,5,Creopening
OL,7,FIran's foreign minister Abbas Araghchi
OL,8,Falso said ships would be allowed to
OL,9,Fpass through the strait over the next
OL,10,Ftwo weeks in "coordination" with the
OL,11,Fcountry's military.
OL,13,FHe said in a statement: "For a period
OL,14,Fof two weeks, safe passage through the
OL,15,FStrait of Hormuz will be possible via
OL,16,Fcoordination with Iran's armed forces
OL,17,Fand with due consideration of
OL,18,Ftechnical limitations."
OL,26,@rD@NOUrD@[O]uD@YOUzD@WO]
