OL,3,CTrump agrees to halt bombing of Iran
OL,4,Cfor two weeks subject to strait
OL,5,Creopening
OL,7,FPrior to the conflict, there were no
OL,8,Frestrictions and it was not clear if
OL,9,FIran would continue to seek to charge
OL,10,Fships as it had been doing during the
OL,11,Fwar.
OL,13,FOn its 10-point plan for the future,
OL,14,FIran also said the strait would be
OL,15,Fsubject to "regulated passage... under
OL,16,Fthe coordination of the armed forces
OL,17,Fof Iran".
OL,19,FIn doing so, it would be "conferring
OL,20,Fupon Iran a unique economic and
OL,21,Fgeopolitical standing".
