OL,7,FThis would appear to be at direct odds
OL,8,Fwith Mr Trump's demand for the
OL,9,Fshipping route to be fully open to
OL,10,Fvessels and flags potential future
OL,11,Fdifficulties to overcome.
OL,13,FIn the face of ongoing military
OL,14,Fstrikes by the US and Israel, Iran has
OL,15,Ftightened its grip on the critical
OL,16,Fshipping route, sending global oil and
OL,17,Fgas prices skyrocketing and causing
OL,18,Fglobal economic uncertainty.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
