OL,3,CTrump agrees to halt bombing of Iran
OL,4,Cfor two weeks subject to strait
OL,5,Creopening
OL,7,FEarlier, ahead of the announced
OL,8,Fceasefire, Mr Trump said: "A whole
OL,9,Fcivilisation will die tonight, never
OL,10,Fto be brought back again.
OL,12,F"I don't want that to happen, but it
OL,13,Fprobably will."
OL,15,FAmong those to criticise his ominous
OL,16,Fthreat was Pope Leo XIV, who branded
OL,17,Fit "truly unacceptable".
